# SwiftUI views

- No business logic or direct persistence in views; use ViewModels/services.
- Localize user-visible strings; avoid hardcoded copy for release UI.
- Add accessibility labels/hints where meaning isn't clear from controls alone.
- Previews use mock data only (no secrets, no production URLs).
